1
00:01:31,820 --> 00:01:34,950
[Wind Direction]

2
00:01:35,580 --> 00:01:37,900
[Episode 12]

3
00:01:39,270 --> 00:01:40,190
Stop crying.

4
00:01:39,729 --> 00:01:42,370
[Winter, 1987]

5
00:01:40,190 --> 00:01:42,650
If you keep crying, I'll leave you like this!

6
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,920
Then just leave me alone!

7
00:01:45,850 --> 00:01:47,470
Oh, you feel wronged, do you?

8
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,470
I told you to just stay by the river and not to move.

9
00:01:49,470 --> 00:01:50,550
But you didn't listen.

10
00:01:50,550 --> 00:01:51,660
You just had to step onto the ice.

11
00:01:51,660 --> 00:01:53,190
Now you fell into the ice hole, didn't you?

12
00:01:53,190 --> 00:01:54,870
Who are you trying to blame here?

13
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:57,270
It's your fault!

14
00:01:57,270 --> 00:01:58,910
Cheng Yaya, listen!

15
00:01:58,910 --> 00:01:59,870
You fell into that hole

16
00:01:59,870 --> 00:02:00,670
on your own.

17
00:02:00,690 --> 00:02:02,410
Don't try to pin it on me.

18
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:03,110
Also,

19
00:02:03,140 --> 00:02:04,600
when Mom and Dad come back later,

20
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:05,080
if you dare to tell them

21
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:06,620
that you fell into the ice hole,

22
00:02:06,620 --> 00:02:07,550
I'll never take you out

23
00:02:07,550 --> 00:02:08,509
to play again.

24
00:02:09,509 --> 00:02:10,789
Did you hear me?

25
00:02:13,390 --> 00:02:14,270
You're a boy.

26
00:02:14,270 --> 00:02:15,390
Aren't you ashamed

27
00:02:15,410 --> 00:02:16,940
of crying all day like this?

28
00:02:21,190 --> 00:02:22,520
Mom, Miaomiao

29
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:25,190
pushed me into an ice hole!

30
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,800
I really didn't push him.

31
00:02:31,910 --> 00:02:33,630
He fell into himself.

32
00:02:33,670 --> 00:02:35,230
I jumped in to save him.

33
00:02:35,340 --> 00:02:37,100
Both Li Si and Hu Qiumin saw it.

34
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,560
Go ask them.

35
00:02:38,950 --> 00:02:40,390
They're on your side.

36
00:02:40,390 --> 00:02:42,190
Why should I bother asking them?

37
00:02:42,670 --> 00:02:43,710
Cheng Miaomiao, let me tell you this.

38
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:45,480
Even if nothing had happened to your brother,

39
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:47,540
you'd still be in for a beating today.

40
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,890
What did I do?

41
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:50,120
You know what you did.

42
00:02:50,130 --> 00:02:50,790
Your homeroom teacher

43
00:02:50,790 --> 00:02:51,750
told me

44
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:53,270
all about your misbehavior at school.

45
00:02:53,270 --> 00:02:54,590
Were you the one who led the charge in telling the teacher

46
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:55,870
that it doesn't matter if we don't get first place?

47
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:57,200
Have you ever said that?

48
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:59,079
Yes, so what?

49
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:00,990
Today, I'll show you exactly

50
00:03:00,990 --> 00:03:01,910
what "so what" means!

51
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:02,510
Come here!

52
00:03:07,850 --> 00:03:10,410
[Hello, Teacher]

53
00:03:10,500 --> 00:03:13,670
[Linqi Oilfield; Social Security Department]

54
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:23,970
Haven't you gone to lunch yet?

55
00:03:27,870 --> 00:03:30,710
You're always so eager when it's time to collect money each month.

56
00:03:30,710 --> 00:03:32,510
Her dad scammed everyone at the factory,

57
00:03:32,510 --> 00:03:33,940
and yet we still have to support her family.

58
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:35,600
What kind of nonsense is that?

59
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,230
What can we do?

60
00:03:38,329 --> 00:03:40,130
Just follow the rules to do this.

61
00:03:43,070 --> 00:03:45,150
Where... is your dad hiding?

62
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,329
I don't know.

63
00:03:57,010 --> 00:03:57,810
Sign here.

64
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:07,840
Aunt,

65
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,160
when can my sister's household registration

66
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:13,440
be processed?

67
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,250
How many times have I told you?

68
00:04:15,250 --> 00:04:17,480
We don't have your parents' marriage certificate

69
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,560
and your sister's birth certificate.

70
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:22,220
How can we process her household registration?

71
00:04:23,790 --> 00:04:25,690
But if she doesn't get registered,

72
00:04:25,690 --> 00:04:26,960
she can't even go to kindergarten.

73
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:27,970
What should we do in the future?

74
00:04:27,970 --> 00:04:29,440
Given your family's circumstances,

75
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:31,120
even if we manage to get her registered,

76
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,510
how will you afford schooling

77
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:33,750
for both of you

78
00:04:34,020 --> 00:04:36,350
on just the factory's monthly allowance?

79
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:39,630
Get out!

80
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,430
You can't do this!

81
00:04:41,430 --> 00:04:42,860
The students are still in class!

82
00:04:42,860 --> 00:04:43,870
It's already like this!

83
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:44,980
What's the point of having class?

84
00:04:44,980 --> 00:04:45,770
Does your school

85
00:04:45,770 --> 00:04:47,170
still adhere to the law?

86
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:47,750
You can't do this!

87
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:48,470
Today,

88
00:04:48,550 --> 00:04:50,350
you must hand over Yuan Yong's child!

89
00:04:50,350 --> 00:04:52,000
Yes, hand her over! Let's go!

90
00:04:54,770 --> 00:04:55,540
Calm down!

91
00:04:55,870 --> 00:04:57,150
Calm down!

92
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:59,790
Listen to me!

93
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:01,910
Listen to me!

94
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:03,590
Listen to me!

95
00:05:04,150 --> 00:05:05,940
The police have already made an inquiry.

96
00:05:05,940 --> 00:05:07,010
They have asked.

97
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:08,750
Yuan Shanqing really doesn't know

98
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:09,980
where Yuan Yong is.

99
00:05:10,230 --> 00:05:11,800
And even if she does, she won't tell us.

100
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,400
The police can't do anything about her.

101
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:15,390
But we... have our own ways!

102
00:05:15,410 --> 00:05:16,920
Yuan Yong couldn't possibly have

103
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,110
spent all our money.

104
00:05:18,140 --> 00:05:18,950
His daughter

105
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:19,870
must be hiding it!

106
00:05:19,870 --> 00:05:20,460
Yes.

107
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:22,070
If she doesn't tell us

108
00:05:22,070 --> 00:05:22,650
where the money is,

109
00:05:22,650 --> 00:05:24,000
no one will have it easy!

110
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:24,950
Yes!

111
00:05:29,890 --> 00:05:31,020
Stop shouting!

112
00:05:37,230 --> 00:05:39,350
Parents, here's the thing.

113
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:40,550
This really isn't a matter

114
00:05:40,550 --> 00:05:41,750
for our school to handle,

115
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:42,510
is it?

116
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,790
And what you're doing

117
00:05:43,790 --> 00:05:44,670
is severely disrupting

118
00:05:44,670 --> 00:05:46,020
our teaching environment

119
00:05:46,020 --> 00:05:47,670
and affecting both the students and the teachers,

120
00:05:47,670 --> 00:05:48,300
right?

121
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:49,470
Parents...

122
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:51,250
-We...
-You're absolutely right.

123
00:05:51,250 --> 00:05:52,130
So...

124
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,830
call her over, and we'll take her away.

125
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:54,930
We won't be in each other's way.

126
00:05:54,930 --> 00:05:56,550
The school should hand her over!

127
00:05:56,550 --> 00:05:57,680
If you can't handle it,

128
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,790
we'll go to the principal!

129
00:05:58,790 --> 00:06:00,190
Yes, go to the principal!

130
00:06:03,330 --> 00:06:04,070
Mom!

131
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:05,610
What are you doing?

132
00:06:05,710 --> 00:06:06,670
This is the school.

133
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:07,560
Isn't it embarrassing?

134
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,950
Yuan Yong did the wicked thing,

135
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:09,430
and he didn't care about shame.

136
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:11,670
So, we're supposed to care about shame here?

137
00:06:11,670 --> 00:06:12,840
Have you forgotten

138
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:14,130
how your grandma died?

139
00:06:14,130 --> 00:06:16,170
But you can't make a scene at school.

140
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,310
See, Mrs. Xiaoli.

141
00:06:17,310 --> 00:06:17,930
Even your son knows

142
00:06:17,930 --> 00:06:19,400
that it's wrong to cause trouble at school.

143
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:20,270
Yes, Mom, let's go back...

144
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:21,430
Shut up!

145
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:23,790
You're siding with outsiders!

146
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:24,910
Don't hit the kid!

147
00:06:24,910 --> 00:06:26,430
Don't hit the kid!

148
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:28,940
My mother-in-law

149
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,860
died

150
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,950
because of this!

151
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:35,920
Our family is in ruins, torn apart!

152
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:42,540
The formula for the slope of a line is...

153
00:06:43,090 --> 00:06:44,600
Luo Zheng's mom has brought people to get you.

154
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,930
You need to hide, quick!

155
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,720
I won't.

156
00:06:51,540 --> 00:06:52,650
What I have to face,

157
00:06:52,670 --> 00:06:53,530
I can't escape.

158
00:06:54,330 --> 00:06:56,360
A wise person knows when to back down.

159
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,470
They're all agitated right now.

160
00:06:57,470 --> 00:06:59,159
You don't know what they might do.

161
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,190
-Say something.
-Yeah.

162
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:00,870
If something really happens to you,

163
00:07:00,870 --> 00:07:01,560
what about Zi?

164
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,310
Let's go.

165
00:07:03,990 --> 00:07:05,470
Look at these people.

166
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,450
Which one of them hasn’t

167
00:07:08,450 --> 00:07:10,470
saved up most of their life’s savings?

168
00:07:10,470 --> 00:07:11,820
Is saving money easy?

169
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:13,490
And now we've lost it all.

170
00:07:14,260 --> 00:07:16,850
I have just one question, Director Xiao.

171
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:18,470
Can you

172
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,630
call Yuan Shanqing over?

173
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:21,920
At the very least, we could ask her

174
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,020
face-to-face.

175
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:27,760
You can't, can you?

176
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:30,380
Okay, I'll find her myself!

177
00:07:30,590 --> 00:07:32,090
I know which classroom she is in!

178
00:07:32,090 --> 00:07:33,020
Mom!

179
00:07:38,170 --> 00:07:39,630
They're coming upstairs.

180
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:42,800
I know where we should go.

181
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,480
Follow me.

182
00:07:44,770 --> 00:07:45,680
You two, stay behind and watch our backs.

183
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,480
Let me know if anything happens.

184
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:09,460
[Astronomy Science Room]

185
00:08:04,380 --> 00:08:04,940
Let's go.

186
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:14,020
No one usually comes here.

187
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:15,670
They definitely won't find us here.

188
00:08:15,670 --> 00:08:16,510
Don't worry.

189
00:08:17,130 --> 00:08:18,930
I haven't even been here before.

190
00:08:19,460 --> 00:08:20,500
Yuan Shanqing!

191
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:23,270
Yuan Shanqing!

192
00:08:24,150 --> 00:08:25,100
Yuan Shanqing!

193
00:08:25,230 --> 00:08:25,780
Mom!

194
00:08:26,450 --> 00:08:27,160
Mom.

195
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:28,450
Son!

196
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:30,230
Where is Yuan Shanqing's seat?

197
00:08:30,230 --> 00:08:32,030
Mom, she's not in the classroom.

198
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:33,669
Not in the classroom?

199
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:35,510
Fine!

200
00:08:36,049 --> 00:08:37,120
I know. I know.

201
00:08:37,340 --> 00:08:39,070
Let's not cause a scene in class.

202
00:08:39,070 --> 00:08:40,270
Not in the classroom?

203
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,110
I don't believe she'll skip class forever!

204
00:08:42,110 --> 00:08:43,390
If she doesn't come today,

205
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:44,720
we'll just wait here!

206
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,630
Yes! Yes!

207
00:08:48,330 --> 00:08:49,350
What are you doing here?

208
00:08:49,350 --> 00:08:50,120
Get out!

209
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,800
This is a school!

210
00:08:51,830 --> 00:08:53,760
This has nothing to do with you two!

211
00:08:53,990 --> 00:08:55,470
If Yuan Shanqing doesn't show up,

212
00:08:55,470 --> 00:08:56,700
we're not leaving today!

213
00:08:56,700 --> 00:08:58,420
Yes, we won't leave!

214
00:08:59,490 --> 00:09:00,560
Calm down, everyone.

215
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:02,000
Parents, parents,

216
00:09:02,070 --> 00:09:02,790
we can't solve anything

217
00:09:02,790 --> 00:09:03,750
like this,

218
00:09:03,750 --> 00:09:04,390
right?

219
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:05,680
Let's go find somewhere

220
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:06,720
to sit down and talk.

221
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,300
It's just an internal conflict among us.

222
00:09:08,300 --> 00:09:09,230
We can settle this peacefully.

223
00:09:09,230 --> 00:09:10,070
Calm down.

224
00:09:11,690 --> 00:09:12,490
Open the door.

225
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:14,630
Miaomiao!

226
00:09:14,650 --> 00:09:15,670
-Hu is here.
-Open the door.

227
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:16,510
Open the door.

228
00:09:17,190 --> 00:09:18,270
Stop shouting!

229
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:19,550
Coming.

230
00:09:19,950 --> 00:09:20,870
Be quiet.

231
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,610
What's going on?

232
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,850
They're still causing a scene.

233
00:09:24,850 --> 00:09:26,030
I've asked Mr. Gao and Ms. Han

234
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:27,190
to go deal with them first.

235
00:09:27,190 --> 00:09:27,870
Ms. Han said

236
00:09:27,870 --> 00:09:30,160
that we wouldn't let Yuan Shanqing go with them.

237
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,090
What about Fang?

238
00:09:31,090 --> 00:09:32,100
What did she say?

239
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,440
I didn't catch it.

240
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,780
When I saw what was happening,

241
00:09:34,780 --> 00:09:35,450
I hurried here

242
00:09:35,450 --> 00:09:36,530
to inform you.

243
00:09:37,990 --> 00:09:39,430
As for Fang's character,

244
00:09:39,650 --> 00:09:41,010
she is so cunning.

245
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:42,320
Let me tell you.

246
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:44,530
She wouldn't dare offend the parents.

247
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:46,850
I just heard the parents talking about

248
00:09:46,850 --> 00:09:48,930
getting Yuan Shanqing expelled.

249
00:09:51,070 --> 00:09:51,760
Oh no.

250
00:09:52,470 --> 00:09:54,590
Fang easily yields under pressure.

251
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:58,090
I don't want to drag the school into this,

252
00:09:58,930 --> 00:10:00,240
or you guys either.

253
00:10:03,150 --> 00:10:05,150
If it comes down to it, I'll just go with them.

254
00:10:05,150 --> 00:10:06,110
Are you stupid?

255
00:10:06,110 --> 00:10:07,110
Where would you go?

256
00:10:07,110 --> 00:10:07,790
What could you possibly do?

257
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:08,930
Can you arrest your dad?

258
00:10:08,930 --> 00:10:10,300
You just stay here.

259
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:11,350
Don't worry.

260
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,240
Nobody knows

261
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:13,220
you're here except us.

262
00:10:13,220 --> 00:10:13,900
Yes.

263
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:16,060
If the school is trying to expel you,

264
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,190
I'll go to the principal

265
00:10:17,190 --> 00:10:18,390
and the factory manager.

266
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:19,460
We'll all go.

267
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:19,990
Yes.

268
00:10:20,470 --> 00:10:21,510
My dad is a leader.

269
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:22,390
He really knows the factory manager.

270
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:23,990
I'll ask him to take us to him.

271
00:10:32,100 --> 00:10:33,630
Everyone inside, come out!

272
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:36,430
Come out.

273
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:38,370
It's... Mr. Gao!

274
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:39,270
I'll go.

275
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,930
You... you go...

276
00:10:41,190 --> 00:10:42,230
Mr. Gao?

277
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:49,770
Mr. Gao.

278
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:57,460
Mr. Gao.

279
00:10:57,630 --> 00:10:59,360
How do you know that we are here?

280
00:10:59,630 --> 00:11:00,710
Li Si told me.

281
00:11:02,940 --> 00:11:05,150
You guys have found a good place.

282
00:11:05,880 --> 00:11:07,540
Playing hide-and-seek here?

283
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:08,910
What's the point of attending class?

284
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:10,510
She's going to be taken away.

285
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,950
With me here, who would dare to take you?

286
00:11:13,950 --> 00:11:14,750
We've driven them away.

287
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:15,680
Go back to class.

288
00:11:15,740 --> 00:11:16,470
Mr. Gao,

289
00:11:17,590 --> 00:11:19,590
