00:22:32,610 --> 00:22:34,350
Otherwise, I won't be able to hold my head up

577
00:22:34,350 --> 00:22:35,790
in front of your Uncle Yang.

578
00:22:35,790 --> 00:22:37,310
I really don't get it.

579
00:22:37,310 --> 00:22:38,220
Why do you always

580
00:22:38,220 --> 00:22:39,630
compare me to my brother?

581
00:22:39,950 --> 00:22:40,990
What's the point?

582
00:22:40,990 --> 00:22:42,190
We're all one family.

583
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:45,390
One family?

584
00:22:45,630 --> 00:22:47,000
Did I give birth to you and him?

585
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:47,490
See?

586
00:22:47,980 --> 00:22:49,610
That's what annoys me about you.

587
00:22:49,610 --> 00:22:50,620
From the bottom of your heart,

588
00:22:50,620 --> 00:22:51,710
you never truly think about us

589
00:22:51,710 --> 00:22:53,440
living together as one family.

590
00:22:54,150 --> 00:22:55,550
If you really can't do it,

591
00:22:55,700 --> 00:22:57,890
just leave Yang Songbai. Divorce him.

592
00:22:58,300 --> 00:22:59,270
I can accept it.

593
00:22:59,300 --> 00:23:01,830
You accept it? What's there for you to accept?

594
00:23:03,050 --> 00:23:04,800
If I get divorced again, I...

595
00:23:07,540 --> 00:23:09,180
Fine, I'm telling you...

596
00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:11,290
It's useless even if I tell you.

597
00:23:11,700 --> 00:23:12,900
Forget it. Let's eat.

598
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:23,180
If it weren't for you...

599
00:23:23,950 --> 00:23:25,910
Mom, let's just eat.

600
00:23:38,950 --> 00:23:41,550
The parent-teacher meeting is coming up, huh?

601
00:23:43,110 --> 00:23:43,830
If I hadn't asked,

602
00:23:43,830 --> 00:23:46,060
you wouldn't have brought it up, would you?

603
00:23:46,060 --> 00:23:46,950
I would have.

604
00:23:47,080 --> 00:23:48,880
I just didn't get the chance yet.

605
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:51,460
How many subjects did you fail this time?

606
00:23:51,770 --> 00:23:52,860
Only two.

607
00:23:53,660 --> 00:23:54,580
Is that so?

608
00:24:00,350 --> 00:24:01,130
Four.

609
00:24:05,100 --> 00:24:06,140
Cheng Miaomiao.

610
00:24:06,910 --> 00:24:07,940
If your brother hadn't told me,

611
00:24:07,940 --> 00:24:10,910
were you planning to change your grades secretly again, right?

612
00:24:10,910 --> 00:24:11,790
I'm not going to embarrass myself by going to the meeting.

613
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:12,790
Ask your dad to go.

614
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:14,630
I'm old.

615
00:24:14,630 --> 00:24:15,720
I'm nearing menopause.

616
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,310
Let me live for a few more years.

617
00:24:17,310 --> 00:24:18,510
What menopause?

618
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:20,760
That doesn't start until women reach their fifties.

619
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:22,800
Cheng Miaomiao, don't you get it?

620
00:24:22,910 --> 00:24:23,700
You've made me so angry

621
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:25,880
that you've brought on my menopause early.

622
00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:27,330
I'll go to your brother's meeting,

623
00:24:27,330 --> 00:24:29,390
and you can ask whoever to go to yours.

624
00:24:31,580 --> 00:24:33,510
It would be better if you did not go.

625
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:40,500
Yuan Shanqing.

626
00:24:41,210 --> 00:24:44,640
Are you really not going to move into the teacher's dormitory?

627
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:46,090
I still have to take care of Zi.

628
00:24:46,090 --> 00:24:48,150
It's more convenient to stay at home.

629
00:24:48,390 --> 00:24:49,670
But what if they come looking for you

630
00:24:49,670 --> 00:24:50,400
at your home?

631
00:24:51,940 --> 00:24:53,380
Actually, I have an idea.

632
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:58,470
Stop talking. The parents are all here.

633
00:24:59,210 --> 00:25:00,200
Alright, I'll run now.

634
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:01,190
If something happens to me,

635
00:25:01,190 --> 00:25:02,110
remember to bring me something to eat

636
00:25:02,110 --> 00:25:02,980
at the arch of the bridge tonight.

637
00:25:02,980 --> 00:25:04,260
My dad has surgery to perform today,

638
00:25:04,260 --> 00:25:05,560
and you know how my mom is.

639
00:25:05,560 --> 00:25:06,710
Let's go to the arch of the bridge tonight too.

640
00:25:06,710 --> 00:25:07,910
You buy some food and bring it to us.

641
00:25:07,910 --> 00:25:09,640
Shouldn't we observe the situation first?

642
00:25:09,640 --> 00:25:10,630
Don't rush off.

643
00:25:10,650 --> 00:25:11,650
Wait for me.

644
00:25:18,980 --> 00:25:19,890
Are you sure?

645
00:25:21,810 --> 00:25:23,010
I want to give it a try.

646
00:25:24,470 --> 00:25:26,350
If I keep staying silent,

647
00:25:26,550 --> 00:25:27,620
no one will ever know

648
00:25:27,620 --> 00:25:28,700
the truth.

649
00:25:30,020 --> 00:25:31,390
It only takes one person

650
00:25:31,500 --> 00:25:33,070
to say that I'm in cahoots with Yuan Yong,

651
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:34,800
and everyone will think so too.

652
00:25:36,380 --> 00:25:37,390
As you said,

653
00:25:37,730 --> 00:25:39,360
it's hard for an innocent man to retain his clean name without explanation.

654
00:25:39,360 --> 00:25:41,890
I still need to explain what I have to explain.

655
00:25:43,870 --> 00:25:44,930
I'm mainly worried

656
00:25:44,930 --> 00:25:46,950
that they'll be unreasonable because there are too many of them.

657
00:25:46,950 --> 00:25:48,010
At least in school,

658
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:49,270
you're safe,

659
00:25:49,910 --> 00:25:51,620
and everyone is on your side.

660
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:53,840
Xiao Fang has also taken a stand.

661
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:56,650
You don't need to worry so much.

662
00:25:57,740 --> 00:25:59,670
I'm really grateful to Director Xiao

663
00:25:59,670 --> 00:26:00,870
and everyone else,

664
00:26:03,610 --> 00:26:04,750
but we can't keep having groups of people

665
00:26:04,750 --> 00:26:06,820
coming to the school and causing trouble like this.

666
00:26:06,820 --> 00:26:07,820
Everyone is affected

667
00:26:07,820 --> 00:26:08,900
because of me.

668
00:26:10,280 --> 00:26:11,330
I don't want that.

669
00:26:15,030 --> 00:26:15,670
Okay.

670
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:17,120
Do it.

671
00:26:17,980 --> 00:26:18,670
Even if only one

672
00:26:18,670 --> 00:26:19,880
out of ten people believes you,

673
00:26:19,880 --> 00:26:21,140
then it means working.

674
00:26:22,580 --> 00:26:23,710
You wait for me here.

675
00:26:23,770 --> 00:26:24,970
No more "You go, I go."

676
00:26:25,470 --> 00:26:26,510
I'll go with you.

677
00:26:27,910 --> 00:26:28,790
When they come out,

678
00:26:28,790 --> 00:26:29,670
watch their expressions.

679
00:26:29,670 --> 00:26:32,600
We'll run immediately if their expressions are off.

680
00:26:32,810 --> 00:26:33,920
It's still early.

681
00:26:33,950 --> 00:26:35,180
Every parent-teacher meeting

682
00:26:35,180 --> 00:26:36,790
lasts at least two hours.

683
00:26:39,610 --> 00:26:40,270
Why don't we

684
00:26:40,280 --> 00:26:41,230
go buy some food?

685
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:43,340
Prepare in advance, just in case.

686
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:44,970
No, no.

687
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:47,550
I've got a bad feeling. I'm leaving.

688
00:26:49,760 --> 00:26:50,890
They're coming out?

689
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:55,590
It shouldn't be.

690
00:26:55,590 --> 00:26:56,850
It's only half an hour.

691
00:26:58,860 --> 00:26:59,900
My dad is out too.

692
00:27:01,100 --> 00:27:02,430
Something's not right.

693
00:27:04,510 --> 00:27:05,100
Miaomiao,

694
00:27:05,100 --> 00:27:06,760
do you think my dad's smiling?

695
00:27:08,510 --> 00:27:09,780
My mom is smiling too.

696
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:14,300
The atmosphere is joyful.

697
00:27:15,630 --> 00:27:17,090
Why am I feeling so scared?

698
00:27:32,620 --> 00:27:34,100
Uncle Lin, I'm sorry.

699
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:35,650
You still dare to come here?

700
00:27:35,830 --> 00:27:37,150
How did I help Yuan Yong?

701
00:27:37,150 --> 00:27:37,910
-Watch out.
-Dad.

702
00:27:37,910 --> 00:27:38,550
I lent him 200 yuan

703
00:27:38,550 --> 00:27:39,430
for one sentence of him.

704
00:27:39,430 --> 00:27:40,580
Calm down. Relax.

705
00:27:40,580 --> 00:27:41,590
We just wanted to apologize,

706
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:42,310
nothing more.

707
00:27:42,310 --> 00:27:43,350
Think about it!

708
00:27:43,390 --> 00:27:44,690
Over the years, how much money have you spent?

709
00:27:44,690 --> 00:27:45,990
Now you're denying it?

710
00:27:45,990 --> 00:27:47,030
What am I denying?

711
00:27:47,030 --> 00:27:48,740
You were the one who said to invest,

712
00:27:48,740 --> 00:27:49,950
and that's why I trusted Yuan Yong!

713
00:27:49,950 --> 00:27:51,150
Now you blame everything on me

714
00:27:51,150 --> 00:27:52,190
and deny everything?

715
00:27:52,190 --> 00:27:53,430
How dare you hit me?

716
00:27:53,430 --> 00:27:54,390
-Uncle.
-How dare you hit me?

717
00:27:54,390 --> 00:27:55,670
-I'll kill you!
-Calm down.

718
00:27:55,670 --> 00:27:56,230
Calm down!

719
00:27:56,230 --> 00:27:56,710
Uncle, aunt!

720
00:27:56,710 --> 00:27:58,340
I'll kill you!

721
00:27:58,340 --> 00:27:59,310
Calm down!

722
00:28:02,850 --> 00:28:03,830
Grandpa, Grandma,

723
00:28:03,830 --> 00:28:06,080
my dad did wrong and broke the law.

724
00:28:06,590 --> 00:28:08,080
But the law will punish him.

725
00:28:08,080 --> 00:28:10,010
I'll definitely not cover for him.

726
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:11,940
I'm also a victim.

727
00:28:12,810 --> 00:28:14,120
Please believe me.

728
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:16,760
Darling,

729
00:28:17,100 --> 00:28:18,940
the girl is really pitiful.

730
00:28:21,660 --> 00:28:23,180
We believe you.

731
00:28:23,780 --> 00:28:25,590
How did this

732
00:28:25,620 --> 00:28:26,420
happen to you?

733
00:28:27,050 --> 00:28:29,620
Well... who is your father?

734
00:28:33,760 --> 00:28:34,350
You...

735
00:28:38,290 --> 00:28:39,570
Coming, Ms. Zhang.

736
00:28:39,600 --> 00:28:41,060
I was just looking for you.

737
00:28:44,250 --> 00:28:46,450
Aunt Wang, I'm sorry.

738
00:28:49,160 --> 00:28:50,260
Actually, about Yuan Yong...

739
00:28:50,260 --> 00:28:50,900
Run!

740
00:28:52,840 --> 00:28:54,410
You two little brats,

741
00:28:54,430 --> 00:28:55,770
you dare to come here yourselves?

742
00:28:55,770 --> 00:28:56,850
You better run.

743
00:28:57,040 --> 00:28:59,410
Run! Keep running!

744
00:29:00,570 --> 00:29:02,020
What the heck!

745
00:29:03,520 --> 00:29:05,540
[Danger; Please Stay Away]

746
00:29:17,370 --> 00:29:19,570
Maybe we were both thinking too simply.

747
00:29:23,670 --> 00:29:24,550
It's okay.

748
00:29:25,470 --> 00:29:26,930
At least, I've faced them.

749
00:29:39,380 --> 00:29:40,020
Let's go.

750
00:29:55,370 --> 00:29:57,170
Here, Grandpa, have some water.

751
00:29:57,570 --> 00:29:58,000
Mr. Gao.

752
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:58,580
It's okay.

753
00:29:58,580 --> 00:29:59,750
Please sit.

754
00:30:00,300 --> 00:30:02,350
Mr. Gao, you see.

755
00:30:02,950 --> 00:30:04,470
I can't read or write.

756
00:30:04,490 --> 00:30:06,260
I also don't know

757
00:30:06,290 --> 00:30:07,650
what you wrote on the blackboard

758
00:30:07,650 --> 00:30:09,290
or the things

759
00:30:09,620 --> 00:30:11,210
you put on your desk.

760
00:30:14,010 --> 00:30:16,280
I was too embarrassed to ask in class.

761
00:30:16,310 --> 00:30:18,350
I was afraid that people would laugh at me.

762
00:30:18,350 --> 00:30:19,110
We wouldn't.

763
00:30:19,410 --> 00:30:20,650
If you have anything you want to know,

764
00:30:20,650 --> 00:30:21,810
just ask me.

765
00:30:23,860 --> 00:30:26,850
How did Qiang Xiaowa do on the exam this time?

766
00:30:27,360 --> 00:30:28,760
What rank did he get?

767
00:30:29,820 --> 00:30:30,690
This time,

768
00:30:31,050 --> 00:30:32,600
he's first in our class.

769
00:30:33,550 --> 00:30:34,110
He...

770
00:30:36,620 --> 00:30:39,070
My Xiaowa is first this time?

771
00:30:43,620 --> 00:30:44,550
This brat,

772
00:30:44,550 --> 00:30:45,870
why didn't he tell me?

773
00:30:47,120 --> 00:30:48,800
I-I-I was just looking around

774
00:30:48,820 --> 00:30:50,220
to see where the ranking was posted,

775
00:30:50,220 --> 00:30:51,570
but I couldn't find it.

776
00:30:52,390 --> 00:30:54,610
We didn't post the rankings in our class this time,

777
00:30:54,610 --> 00:30:55,620
nor did I announce

778
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:57,500
the rankings in the class either.

779
00:30:57,910 --> 00:31:01,310
I think the ranking isn't important.

780
00:31:01,710 --> 00:31:02,790
What's important is

781
00:31:02,790 --> 00:31:03,990
that the children are really learning

782
00:31:03,990 --> 00:31:04,980
knowledge

783
00:31:05,250 --> 00:31:06,960
and staying passionate about their studies.

784
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:07,800
Yes. Yes.

785
00:31:07,850 --> 00:31:09,130
You're right.

786
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,170
You're right.

787
00:31:11,030 --> 00:31:12,430
How does he behave

788
00:31:12,430 --> 00:31:12,950
in school?

789
00:31:12,950 --> 00:31:14,690
He didn't cause any trouble, did he?

790
00:31:14,690 --> 00:31:15,880
You can rest assured.

791
00:31:15,880 --> 00:31:17,260
Xiaowa is very well-behaved.

792
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:19,140
He's doing very well in school.

793
00:31:20,490 --> 00:31:21,860
That's good.

794
00:31:22,860 --> 00:31:23,700
I was

795
00:31:23,700 --> 00:31:24,830
feeling a bit anxious earlier,

796
00:31:24,830 --> 00:31:25,850
worried that he might

797
00:31:25,850 --> 00:31:27,670
cause some trouble for the school.

798
00:31:27,670 --> 00:31:28,600
You know

799
00:31:29,070 --> 00:31:30,350
that we folks from the countryside

800
00:31:30,350 --> 00:31:32,120
don't know the proper manners.

801
00:31:32,150 --> 00:31:33,940
What countryside?

802
00:31:34,150 --> 00:31:34,830
We're all from Heping Town,

803
00:31:34,830 --> 00:31:35,930
aren't we?

804
00:31:36,990 --> 00:31:38,470
Come over here more often if you have the time.

805
00:31:38,470 --> 00:31:39,310
Let Xiaowa show you around

806
00:31:39,310 --> 00:31:40,480
our school.

807
00:31:41,750 --> 00:31:43,100
The food in our school cafeteria

808
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:44,010
is quite good.

809
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:44,780
I've got meal tickets.

810
00:31:44,780 --> 00:31:45,690
My treat.

811
00:31:46,060 --> 00:31:46,600
-Come on.
-Okay.

812
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:47,350
Take it, Grandpa.

813
00:31:47,350 --> 00:31:47,990
Okay.

814
00:31:48,410 --> 00:31:49,090
No.

815
00:31:49,110 --> 00:31:50,230
How can I

816
00:31:50,230 --> 00:31:51,290
let you pay for my meal?

817
00:31:51,290 --> 00:31:52,840
Please take it. It's okay.

818
00:31:52,930 --> 00:31:53,530
I...

819
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:55,080
I don't know what to say.

820
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:57,170
Mr. Gao.

821
00:31:59,720 --> 00:32:01,180
Thank you for everything.

822
00:32:04,630 --> 00:32:06,030
Don't be like this.

823
00:32:06,490 --> 00:32:08,500
It's my duty as a teacher.

824
00:32:09,090 --> 00:32:09,850
Mr. Gao.

825
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:11,400
In my heart, Xiaowa...

826
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:19,260
Here, Mr. Gao.

827
00:32:19,540 --> 00:32:21,180
I caught the seafood myself.

828
00:32:21,210 --> 00:32:22,340
It's not worth much.

829
00:32:22,410 --> 00:32:23,750
Please try it.

830
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:24,800
Hope you like it.

831
00:32:39,390 --> 00:32:40,190
Qiang Xiaowa.

832
00:32:41,940 --> 00:32:42,690
Mr. Gao.

833
00:32:45,730 --> 00:32:47,990
I bought some seafood from your grandpa.

834
00:32:48,050 --> 00:32:49,350
But I forgot to give him money

835
00:32:49,350 --> 00:32:51,150
while a parent was talking to me.

836
00:32:52,210 --> 00:32:53,740
Take the money to him for me.

837
00:33:02,050 --> 00:33:03,680
My younger brother isn't in good health.

838
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:05,880
My mom says that seafood is nutritious.

839
00:33:06,290 --> 00:33:07,560
From now on, I'll buy 50 yuan worth of seafood

840
00:33:07,560 --> 00:33:09,220
from your family every month.

841
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:10,970
You have set some aside for me.

842
00:33:13,420 --> 00:33:15,100
Thank you, Mr. Gao.

843
00:33:16,050 --> 00:33:16,850
Mr. Gao...

844
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:17,840
Keep moping.

845
00:33:30,800 --> 00:33:33,070
Don't just eat meat. Have some vegetables.

846
00:33:33,070 --> 00:33:33,630
Okay.

847
00:33:36,190 --> 00:33:37,640
Some units have already begun

848
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:39,570
implementing the "suspension of salary but retention of position" policy, right?

849
00:33:39,570 --> 00:33:40,650
We have to follow the rules to do it.

850
00:33:40,650 --> 00:33:42,440
It's not like whoever wants it and can have it.

851
00:33:42,440 --> 00:33:43,130
So, what's the current policy

852
00:33:43,130 --> 00:33:44,100
at your unit?

853
00:33:44,370 --> 00:33:45,230
Why did you ask?

854
00:33:46,340 --> 00:33:47,880
Don't you know Ms. Wang?

855
00:33:47,910 --> 00:33:49,370
Her husband asked me to see

856
00:33:50,010 --> 00:33:50,870
if it's possible to retain her position.

857
00:33:50,870 --> 00:33:52,200
This woman is so annoying,

858
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:53,660
always trying to pull strings

859
00:33:53,660 --> 00:33:55,190
and get special treatment.

860
00:33:57,850 --> 00:33:58,930
What's wrong, Si?

861
00:33:59,240 --> 00:34:00,140
Why don't you eat?

862
00:34:00,140 --> 00:34:00,790
I'm eating.

863
00:34:00,790 --> 00:34:01,720
Don't like the dishes?

864
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:02,780
No, no, I like them.

865
00:34:04,730 --> 00:34:05,610
Have some tofu.

866
00:34:05,990 --> 00:34:06,990
Get some protein.

867
00:34:08,520 --> 00:34:09,860
You can't play me like this.

868
00:34:09,860 --> 00:34:10,940
It's too scary.

869
00:34:10,969 --> 00:34:12,330
What's scary about having dinner?

870
00:34:12,330 --> 00:34:13,210
What are you afraid of?

871
00:34:13,210 --> 00:34:14,909
No, it's just... at a time like this,

872
00:34:14,909 --> 00:34:16,280
how can we just eat?

873
00:34:16,310 --> 00:34:18,250
Don't you have anything to say to me?

874
00:34:18,250 --> 00:34:19,440
What, do your mom and I need to

875
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:21,440
involve you when we talk about work?

876
00:34:21,650 --> 00:34:23,130
No, well...

877
00:34:23,540 --> 00:34:24,469
Well...

878
00:34:25,650 --> 00:34:27,820
Well, today...

879
00:34:28,060 --> 00:34:30,120
The parent-teacher meeting, right?

880
00:34:30,810 --> 00:34:32,280
Your teacher told me.

881
00:34:33,030 --> 00:34:34,560
He said that your grades...

882
00:34:35,010 --> 00:34:35,870
have improved,

883
00:34:36,310 --> 00:34:38,840
but there's still room for more improvement.

884
00:34:38,850 --> 00:34:40,310
Son, you have to keep up the good work

885
00:34:40,310 --> 00:34:41,170
and not give up.

886
00:34:41,719 --> 00:34:42,340
I won't give up.

887
00:34:42,340 --> 00:34:43,110
Keep studying hard.

888
00:34:43,110 --> 00:34:43,750
I will.

889
00:34:45,090 --> 00:34:46,010
I didn't really study that hard.

890
00:34:46,010 --> 00:34:46,780
Mostly, I...

891
00:34:48,190 --> 00:34:49,100
The God of Wealth has blessed me this time.

892
00:34:49,100 --> 00:34:50,540
I'll go light some incense for him.

893
00:34:50,540 --> 00:34:52,139
What incense!

894
00:34:52,420 --> 00:34:53,550
Just focus on making progress.

895
00:34:53,550 --> 00:34:54,310
Burn incense?

896
00:34:54,310 --> 00:34:55,030
Don't be so superstitious

897
00:34:55,030 --> 00:34:55,969
like your mom,

898
00:34:55,989 --> 00:34:56,590
got it?

899
00:34:57,310 --> 00:34:57,950
Okay.

900
00:34:58,120 --> 00:34:59,160
Let me summarize.

901
00:35:01,190 --> 00:35:03,520
The improvement in your grades this time,

902
00:35:03,770 --> 00:35:04,760
I don't think...

903
00:35:06,070 --> 00:35:07,200
it's a coincidence.

904
00:35:07,980 --> 00:35:09,220
To a large extent,

905
00:35:09,250 --> 00:35:09,980
I think this is a reason.

906
00:35:09,980 --> 00:35:11,700
I think you've already

907
00:35:12,470 --> 00:35:14,180
that... that...

908
00:35:14,210 --> 00:35:15,670
started inheriting my genes.

909
00:35:15,670 --> 00:35:16,390
Really?

910
00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:18,160
Your IQ is increasing now.

911
00:35:18,570 --> 00:35:19,260
But...

912
00:35:20,820 --> 00:35:22,280
you can't settle for that.

913
00:35:22,450 --> 00:35:23,090
Right?

914
00:35:23,570 --> 00:35:26,900
An innate advantage will eventually become a disadvantage

915
00:35:27,770 --> 00:35:29,430
if you don’t put in the effort.

916
00:35:30,310 --> 00:35:32,630
-You can only rely on yourself.
-Listen carefully.

917
00:35:32,630 --> 00:35:33,890
There are no shortcuts

918
00:35:34,270 --> 00:35:35,530
to achieving success.

919
00:35:36,460 --> 00:35:37,470
-Good!
-Good.

920
00:35:37,490 --> 00:35:38,050
Good.

921
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:45,640
Mom.

922
00:36:04,770 --> 00:36:07,770
I was too strict with you before.

923
00:36:08,970 --> 00:36:10,290
I apologize.

924
00:36:18,970 --> 00:36:19,770
Miaomiao,

925
00:36:21,550 --> 00:36:22,560
do you know

926
00:36:22,580 --> 00:36:25,840
the difference between growing up and achieving success?

927
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:31,990
You're all supposed to have a clear idea

928
00:36:31,990 --> 00:36:33,900
about the results of the baseline test this time.

929
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:35,320
The rankings aren't important,

930
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:38,050
but if you didn't do well, you just didn't do well.

931
00:36:38,100 --> 00:36:40,270
Failing a subject comes with consequences.

932
00:36:40,270 --> 00:36:41,510
For whichever subject you failed,

933
00:36:41,510 --> 00:36:43,480
you should copy that test paper ten times.

934
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:45,790
After you finish, hand it over to Zhu Chao.

935
00:36:45,790 --> 00:36:47,250
I'll personally check it.

936
00:36:49,530 --> 00:36:50,420
What?

937
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:52,440
Ten times.

938
00:36:54,370 --> 00:36:55,130
Li Si,

939
00:36:55,940 --> 00:36:57,650
you copy all the test papers ten times

940
00:36:57,650 --> 00:36:58,910
and the textbook once.

941
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:00,610
Mr. Gao,

942
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:02,430
I didn't fail any subject.

943
00:37:02,430 --> 00:37:03,270
Don't you like

944
00:37:03,300 --> 00:37:04,880
learning from your deskmate?

945
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:06,810
Copy your deskmate's answers ten times

946
00:37:06,810 --> 00:37:07,930
to keep learning.

947
00:37:08,390 --> 00:37:10,830
From now on, anyone in our class caught cheating on an exam

948
00:37:10,830 --> 00:37:12,760
will receive the same punishment.

949
00:37:14,950 --> 00:37:15,620
Copying this much...

950
00:37:15,620 --> 00:37:16,820
When will it ever end?

951
00:37:16,990 --> 00:37:18,730
My hand's going to be crippled.

952
00:37:21,330 --> 00:37:22,790
Your workload is nothing.

953
00:37:24,140 --> 00:37:26,050
When will I ever finish copying?

954
00:37:27,530 --> 00:37:29,130
For the first time in my life,

955
00:37:29,130 --> 00:37:30,480
I had the thought

956
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:32,900
that failing an exam is truly frightening.

957
00:37:34,430 --> 00:37:35,430
God,

958
00:37:35,430 --> 00:37:37,350
please bless me.

959
00:37:37,350 --> 00:37:40,030
Please bless me to pass the next exam.

960
00:37:40,060 --> 00:37:41,610
Please bless my hand.

961
00:37:42,100 --> 00:37:43,330
What's the use of relying on God?

962
00:37:43,330 --> 00:37:45,130
We should rely on ourselves, Si.

963
00:37:46,570 --> 00:37:48,630
I thought God had favored me this time

964
00:37:48,820 --> 00:37:50,750
by helping me escape Li Dahai's beatings,

965
00:37:50,750 --> 00:37:53,410
but I didn't escape Gao Feiyang's punishments.

966
00:37:54,410 --> 00:37:55,680
Well, what exactly

967
00:37:55,710 --> 00:37:56,830
did Gao Feiyang say to our parents

968
00:37:56,830 --> 00:37:58,020
at that parent-teacher meeting?

969
00:37:58,020 --> 00:37:59,300
I don't know either.

970
00:38:00,470 --> 00:38:02,980
I graduated from university just three years ago.

971
00:38:02,980 --> 00:38:04,260
I know many of you

972
00:38:04,310 --> 00:38:05,300
are worried about this.

973
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:10,390
[A Warm Welcome to the Parents of 11th Grade]

974
00:38:06,050 --> 00:38:07,380
You're worried that I don't have enough experience

975
00:38:07,380 --> 00:38:09,910
and won't be able to teach your children well.

976
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,210
I wasn't exactly

977
00:38:11,240 --> 00:38:13,040
a good student myself back then.

978
00:38:13,040 --> 00:38:15,800
The reason I went to a teacher's college was simple,

979
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:18,150
and that's that it didn't charge tuition.

980
00:38:19,610 --> 00:38:21,260
Our family relies on a single income,

981
00:38:21,260 --> 00:38:22,590
and I have a younger brother

982
00:38:22,590 --> 00:38:24,990
who has been sick often since he was little.

983
00:38:25,310 --> 00:38:26,830
I just wanted to

984
00:38:26,850 --> 00:38:28,660
lighten the financial burden on my family.

985
00:38:28,660 --> 00:38:29,810
A teacher

986
00:38:29,830 --> 00:38:31,270
can achieve success

987
00:38:31,300 --> 00:38:32,730
through years of experience,

988
00:38:32,730 --> 00:38:34,980
but I hold myself to a different standard:

989
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:36,640
effective teaching methods.

990
00:38:36,710 --> 00:38:37,640
Mr. Gao,

991
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:38,750
given the limited educational resources

992
00:38:38,750 --> 00:38:39,950
here in the oilfield,

993
00:38:40,430 --> 00:38:41,710
what methods

994
00:38:41,740 --> 00:38:43,100
can be truly effective?

995
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:45,550
That's right. What are they?

996
00:38:45,850 --> 00:38:47,290
Let the kids know

997
00:38:47,680 --> 00:38:49,080
the meaning of learning.

998
00:38:51,270 --> 00:38:52,760
Actually, studying

999
00:38:53,450 --> 00:38:54,930
is incredibly dull

1000
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:56,870
and boring.

1001
00:38:57,420 --> 00:38:58,460
It's hard.

1002
00:38:59,560 --> 00:39:00,720
But it's also

1003
00:39:00,980 --> 00:39:02,840
one of the few things in this world

1004
00:39:03,550 --> 00:39:04,550
where, if you invest effort,

1005
00:39:04,550 --> 00:39:06,110
you can see results.

1006
00:39:06,750 --> 00:39:07,860
It's fair

1007
00:39:08,500 --> 00:39:09,510
and valuable.

1008
00:39:10,270 --> 00:39:11,510
The meaning of learning

1009
00:39:11,510 --> 00:39:13,470
is not about getting perfect scores

1010
00:39:13,470 --> 00:39:14,730
or being ranked first.

1011
00:39:15,220 --> 00:39:16,110
It's about

1012
00:39:16,130 --> 00:39:18,210
that learning allows you to acquire knowledge and wisdom,

1013
00:39:18,210 --> 00:39:20,590
to abandon your ignorance and stubbornness,

1014
00:39:20,590 --> 00:39:21,860
and to see that this world

1015
00:39:21,860 --> 00:39:23,090
is full of diversity.

1016
00:39:24,040 --> 00:39:25,920
As teachers and parents,

1017
00:39:26,820 --> 00:39:27,690
we can't

1018
00:39:27,720 --> 00:39:29,000
just push our children

1019
00:39:29,590 --> 00:39:30,660
to study.

1020
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:33,380
Instead, we should

1021
00:39:33,400 --> 00:39:34,430
make accompanying them in learning

1022
00:39:34,430 --> 00:39:35,690
a part of their growth.

1023
00:39:36,070 --> 00:39:37,870
We should clarify their dreams,

1024
00:39:37,940 --> 00:39:40,140
understand their hopes for the future,

1025
00:39:40,370 --> 00:39:42,080
find the directions of their lives with them,

1026
00:39:42,080 --> 00:39:43,050
and guide them

1027
00:39:43,070 --> 00:39:44,790
step by step

1028
00:39:45,100 --> 00:39:46,700
toward where they want to go.

1029
00:39:48,830 --> 00:39:50,290
We were all once children,

1030
00:39:50,810 --> 00:39:52,050
but let's not forget

1031
00:39:52,250 --> 00:39:53,910
the essence of what a child is.

1032
00:39:54,370 --> 00:39:55,930
A child's growth

1033
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:58,390
shouldn't only revolve around homework and exams,

1034
00:39:58,390 --> 00:39:59,470
nor should it just be

1035
00:39:59,470 --> 00:40:00,630
about indulgence

1036
00:40:00,630 --> 00:40:01,760
and being pampered.

1037
00:40:01,790 --> 00:40:03,550
Figuring out

1038
00:40:04,480 --> 00:40:05,980
what kind of person they want to become

1039
00:40:05,980 --> 00:40:07,910
is also a crucial lesson in their growth.

1040
00:40:07,910 --> 00:40:09,040
But Mr. Gao,

1041
00:40:09,270 --> 00:40:10,620
the test results

1042
00:40:10,650 --> 00:40:12,880
are the standard for evaluation, aren't they?

1043
00:40:12,880 --> 00:40:14,160
Right? -Right.

1044
00:40:16,410 --> 00:40:18,960
We can only say that it's one of the standards.

1045
00:40:20,070 --> 00:40:21,550
I know you are here today

1046
00:40:21,860 --> 00:40:23,030
to see your children's

1047
00:40:23,030 --> 00:40:23,880
exam results.

1048
00:40:23,970 --> 00:40:25,130
That's right.

1049
00:40:25,810 --> 00:40:27,810
But I don't intend to announce them.

1050
00:40:27,910 --> 00:40:28,880
One exam

1051
00:40:28,900 --> 00:40:30,270
doesn't mean anything.

1052
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:32,330
Rankings are meaningless.

1053
00:40:32,570 --> 00:40:33,820
For someone to come in first,

1054
00:40:33,820 --> 00:40:35,550
someone else must come in last.

1055
00:40:35,940 --> 00:40:37,510
But the child who comes in last

1056
00:40:37,510 --> 00:40:39,640
still deserves to have their own life.

1057
00:40:40,170 --> 00:40:41,720
Growth is growth.

1058
00:40:41,760 --> 00:40:42,950
It doesn't mean success.

1059
00:40:42,950 --> 00:40:44,680
They are two different things,

1060
00:40:44,720 --> 00:40:47,120
yet we often mistake them for being the same.

1061
00:40:47,120 --> 00:40:48,780
For the students who didn't do well this time,

1062
00:40:48,780 --> 00:40:50,310
I won't let them off easily.

1063
00:40:50,340 --> 00:40:51,260
I won't go easy on them.

1064
00:40:51,260 --> 00:40:52,060
This is my job

1065
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:52,980
and my duty.

1066
00:40:54,060 --> 00:40:55,860
But I hope that when they go home,

1067
00:40:55,910 --> 00:40:57,510
they feel relaxed and happy.

1068
00:40:58,330 --> 00:40:59,990
Because there has to be a place

1069
00:41:00,100 --> 00:41:01,530
where they can let go

1070
00:41:01,650 --> 00:41:03,450
of all the burdens of this world.

1071
00:41:04,170 --> 00:41:05,050
In school,

1072
00:41:05,690 --> 00:41:06,820
they are students.

1073
00:41:07,130 --> 00:41:09,050
They can't be late or leave early,

1074
00:41:09,450 --> 00:41:12,110
and they have to give their best effort to learn.

1075
00:41:12,210 --> 00:41:13,470
But when they get home,

1076
00:41:14,390 --> 00:41:16,070
they are your children.

1077
00:41:16,930 --> 00:41:18,080
So, as children,

1078
00:41:18,110 --> 00:41:19,190
they should have

1079
00:41:19,220 --> 00:41:21,220
the nature and the rights of a child.

1080
00:41:22,650 --> 00:41:23,600
I think

1081
00:41:23,700 --> 00:41:25,760
that not all teachers are qualified,

1082
00:41:26,220 --> 00:41:27,370
and

1083
00:41:27,410 --> 00:41:28,270
so are parents.

1084
00:41:28,990 --> 00:41:30,670
So, I hope

1085
00:41:32,410 --> 00:41:34,010
that we can trust each other.

1086
00:41:35,740 --> 00:41:37,110
Please trust me.

1087
00:41:37,860 --> 00:41:39,530
I will be a good teacher

1088
00:41:39,920 --> 00:41:42,380
and take responsibility for your children.

1089
00:41:42,480 --> 00:41:43,680
And I trust that you

1090
00:41:43,980 --> 00:41:45,220
will be good parents

1091
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:47,450
and treat my students well.

1092
00:41:51,470 --> 00:41:52,620
Thank you, all parents,

1093
00:41:52,620 --> 00:41:54,650
for attending the parent-teacher meeting of Grade 11, Class 1.

1094
00:41:54,650 --> 00:41:57,210
That's all for today's meeting.

1095
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:09,700
[trust each other; achieve each other]

1096
00:42:12,160 --> 00:42:14,110
We all found out much later

1097
00:42:14,500 --> 00:42:16,570
that this particular parent-teacher meeting

1098
00:42:16,570 --> 00:42:18,200
would turn out to be like this.

1099
00:42:18,200 --> 00:42:19,560
That was also our first time to encounter a parent-teacher meeting

1100
00:42:19,560 --> 00:42:20,630
where no exam papers were handed out

1101
00:42:20,630 --> 00:42:22,430
and no rankings were announced.

1102
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:24,730
Parent-teacher meetings were always a nightmare

1103
00:42:24,730 --> 00:42:25,930
when we were kids.

1104
00:42:26,420 --> 00:42:27,990
You never knew

1105
00:42:28,020 --> 00:42:29,360
what the teacher would say to your parents,

1106
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:30,620
because none of us were

1107
00:42:30,630 --> 00:42:31,340
the kind of kids

1108
00:42:31,340 --> 00:42:32,740
who never made mistakes.

1109
00:42:33,650 --> 00:42:34,930
Gao Feiyang

1110
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:36,620
had a certain magic about him.

1111
00:42:36,770 --> 00:42:38,860
He could always make you realize, in the coolest way,

1112
00:42:38,860 --> 00:42:41,260
that there's another way to look at things.

1113
00:42:41,520 --> 00:42:42,670
He could tell you those grand principles

1114
00:42:42,670 --> 00:42:45,210
in a gentle and touching way.

1115
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:46,850
Gao Feiyang became

1116
00:42:46,850 --> 00:42:47,620
the biggest backer

1117
00:42:47,620 --> 00:42:48,790
of our kids.

1118
00:42:49,650 --> 00:42:51,180
We were willing to trust him

1119
00:42:51,270 --> 00:42:52,390
because we knew

1120
00:42:52,570 --> 00:42:53,970
he cared about us deeply.

1121
00:42:54,470 --> 00:42:56,530
But we were also all terrified of him.

1122
00:42:56,970 --> 00:42:58,050
We were afraid

1123
00:42:58,770 --> 00:43:00,970
that if we didn't become better people,

1124
00:43:01,040 --> 00:43:02,000
we would let him down.
